title: 12/05/2012 - The Church Of What's Happening Now #36
description:
Joey and Lee talk about the Son's of Anarchy Finale, taking chances in life, and we get another surprise visit from Mrs. Diaz. Joey also shows everyone where he got the saying, "Stay Black" from. Joey's friend Sal Polisi calls in to talk about his new book and his time in the mob. 


This show is brought to you by Onnit.com Use the Promo code CHURCH for an extra discount.
